sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Client
  participant AuthController
  participant EmailRateLimiter
  participant Redis


  Client->>AuthController: POST /api/auth/resend-verification or /forgot-password
  AuthController->>EmailRateLimiter: withRateLimit(email) { action }
  EmailRateLimiter->>Redis: EVAL email_rate_limit.lua (rateLimitKey, attemptCountKey)

  alt Rate limited
    Redis-->>EmailRateLimiter: { -1, ttl }
    EmailRateLimiter-->>AuthController: throw RateLimitException(ttl)
    AuthController-->>Client: 429 Too Many Requests
  else Allowed
    Redis-->>EmailRateLimiter: { attemptCount, 0 }
    EmailRateLimiter-->>AuthController: proceed with action
    AuthController-->>Client: 200 OK (or action result)
  end

  Note over Redis: Backoff windows are 60s, 300s, 3600s
